{
  "stem": "27687.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in that-- that was for the SS, and for the German descent people what were working there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And where my train went by, that was in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were garbage cans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And one time, when I drove by, I saw something in the garbage cans what looked like food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I went off, and I made like I cleaned the rails, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then slowly, slowly, I went to the garbage cans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that there were salad and cabbage pieces.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- the middle of cabbage-- and some red beets and so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I filled up my pockets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the next train who came-- and then I cleaned till the next train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I went on the train, I went further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I had to eat it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I went into another building, which looked to me like an old building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Nobody was doing nothing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And probably was ready to be destroyed, that part of the building, because they slowly came, you know, to dig there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was sitting in that building and I was eating my-- the cabbage, and whatever I got.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It took a while.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In the meantime, they were looking for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when I came out, the SS man was yelling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It wasn't SS, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "At that time all the firemen-- the captain was the boss, and then all the rest were old firemen-- with guns, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they were our guarders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was yelling at me, and said, well, I have to report you, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told him, I just went to make pee, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, why didn't you go then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, because I came with-- with the train, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I needed to go pee.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
